## **Summary of Terms**
In summary, these TikTok Shop Developer Terms of Service are a contract between You and **++TikTok Technology Limited++** which govern the provision of TikTok Shop Developer Services to facilitate any development work carried out, by You, to integrate and connect Your services or a seller You provide services to with the TikTok Shop Partner Center platform or any other TikTok Shop platform. Among other things, these Developer Terms:

