* set out some rules as to what You can and cannot do when accessing or using the Developer Services (clause 3);
* set out how TikTok may restrict, suspend (clause 5) or terminate (clause 7) Your access to or use of the Developer Services;
* limit losses that TikTok would otherwise be liable for (clause 10);
* require You to maintain insurance at Your own cost to cover potential liabilities that may arise in connection with access to and use of the Developer Services (clause 11.1); and
* set out how You can resolve any disputes You might have against TikTok under these Developer Terms (clause 11.8).


