By accepting these Developer Terms or by otherwise downloading, installing, accessing, using or operating the TikTok Shop Developer Services, You agree that You have read, and that You agree to be bound by these Developer Terms. If You do not agree to these Developer Terms, You must not access or use the TikTok Shop Developer Services.

